| Function             | Arduino UNO Pin | Suggested ESP32 GPIO |
| -------------------- | --------------- | -------------------- |
| CO (MICS-6814)       | A0              | GPIO34               |
| NH₃ (MICS-6814)      | A1              | GPIO35               |
| NO₂ (MICS-6814)      | A2              | GPIO32               |
| Dust Sensor Vo       | A0              | GPIO33               |
| Dust LED Control     | D2              | GPIO27               |
| GPS RX (from GPS TX) | D4              | GPIO16 (UART1 RX)    |
| GPS TX (to GPS RX)   | D3              | GPIO17 (UART1 TX)    |
